  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective chart review/data collection study of the per oral endoscopic myotomy
      (POEM) procedure, that will include questionnaires administered throughout the study.
      Subjects enrolled will be those intending to have a POEM procedure. Data will be collected
      and reviewed through 12 months post-op.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
